results.deck: A group of Doom modders whose work was featured in Final Doom.
results.description:
TeamTNT created the TNT: Evilution portion of Final Doom. The content was originally developed as a free megawad but shortly before release was bought by id Software to use in Final Doom.
Â 
The group continued to produce free maps, including several multiplayer and singleplayer megawads. TeamTNT also developed the Boom source port, a project intended to fix bugs and limitations in the original Doom while maintaining the original spirit. Essentially making the engine mapper-friendly without focusing on graphical enhancements.
